blurt 1.0 AutoBR.pm
===========================

A plugin for blurt 1.0 that converts double new lines in post content
to <br /><br />, if the post doesn't contain any <br> tags.

By Matthijs de Jonge (rhmtts@gmail.com).

This software is public domain software: do with it whatever you want.


INSTALL:
========

- Upload AutoBR.pm to the plugins directory of your blurt
  installation on the server

VARIABLES:
==========

None.
